<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM1.9.8">
<l>mūttavai kāṇa mutumaṇaṟ kuṉṟēṟi</l>
<l>kūttuvan tāṭik kuḻalāl icaipāṭi</l>
<l>vāytta maṟaiyōr vaṇaṅka vimaiyava</l>
<l>rēttavan teṉṉaip puṟampulkuvāṉ</l>
<l rend="indent">empirāṉ eṉṉaip puṟampulkuvāṉ.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Climbing the old sand hill so that the ancient assembly saw,</l>
<l>delightedly dancing a dance, [and] singing a tune</l>
<l>with [his] flute while the men of the Vedas</l>
<l>who approached bow [to him and] immortals praise [him],</l>
<l>he will come and embrace me from behind.</l>
<l>Our Lord will embrace me from behind.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
